Name: TIM4_Configured
Desc: true or false; flag_to only run this func once

Name: TIM4_Int_Counter
Desc: reset when limit hit, limit is -0x80000000

Name: DMA1C7_??
Desc: set when dma1 ch7 int hit;

Name: TIM4_C?
Desc: counter; checked against 0xea60 which is not a limit

Name: TIM4_??
Desc: set when TIM4_C? reaches 0xea60 in int (60000)

Name: TIM4_Flag_1
Desc: read in int: =1 if (FLAG_1=0 or FLAG_2!=1) else 0
